        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To integrate BGE M3, use frameworks like FastAPI or Flask with Hugging Face's Transformers library. Implement batch processing endpoints to maximize throughput and reduce per-request overhead. Ensure GPU acceleration is enabled for optimal performance."
          }
        ]
      },
