        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For production, consider model quantization to INT8 for further latency reduction. Implement caching for frequent embedding requests and monitor API metrics to auto-scale based on load. Regularly update to the latest model versions to incorporate performance improvements."
